title: Ebro In The Morning - Corpse In The Club + 2022 Grammy Recap & Reggae Controversy
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 4/4/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the 2022 Grammys, a corpse in the club, and controversy over reggae. 

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and get the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
